<div id="news_text">
  <div><h4>ArtSpan Open Studios 2010</h4></div>
  <div>
    <p>During ArtSpan's Open Studios, Mission artists are open on weekend 1 which is October 9-10.  Just like the spring, you can expect hundreds of Mission Artists to open their studios to the public for the weekend.  Art lovers from all over come to see the creativity and innovation of their favorite local artists in our favorite San Francisco neighborhood.</p>
  <p>
    <span class="title">Art Lovers:</span> Mark your calendar for October 09 & 10, 11am - 6pm.
  </p>
  <p>
   <a href="/artists/map?osonly=on" >Click here to see a map of participating Mission Aritsts United Artists</a></p>
  <p>
	Read <a href="/main/openstudios">this</a> for more about what Open Studios is.
  </p>
  <p>
Artists:
	Make sure you've set the Open Studios setting on your profile so you can get properly listed in Open Studios maps/lists on this site.  
<% if logged_in? -%>
Click <a href="<%= artist_path(current_artist) %>/edit#events"/>here<a/> to check your status.
<% else -%>
<a href="/login">Login</a> and check your profile page to make sure your Open Studios status is correct.  If you are doing Open Studios, you should see an OpenStudios star over your profile picture.
<% end-%>
  </p>
